Function to merge payload sent over CAN from SAM

Function is called for as long until payload is available in one structure. Called in functions _fromSAM where Message_Number is a number of a UHF_Sensor message in range from 1 to 9 that UHF is about to merge. Once merge process is complete data is sent to FDH or to Kessy via calling proper functions.
Called externally when payload is sent from SAM
